<view class="page"><view class="nav" style="padding-top:{{navTop}}px;height:{{navHeight}}px"><view bindtap="goBack"><image src="{{icons.back}}"/><text>分班确认</text></view></view><scroll-view class="scroll" scroll-y enhanced show-scrollbar="{{false}}"><view style="height:{{navSpacer}}px"></view><view class="content"><text class="subtitle">确认学员分班信息并发送通知</text>
<view class="student"><image src="{{avatar}}" mode="aspectFill"/><view><view><text>刘承宇</text><text>♂</text><text>10岁</text></view><text>学员编号　SXF202400126</text><view class="state"><view></view><text>在读 · 累计24课时</text></view></view><view class="split"></view><view class="change"><view><text>原状态</text><text>待分班</text></view><text>→</text><view><text>目标班级</text><text>U8启蒙级</text></view></view></view>
<view class="section-title"><view class="mini">班</view><text>班级信息</text></view><view class="class-card"><view class="class-top"><image src="{{classImage}}" mode="aspectFill"/><view class="class-main"><view><text>U8启蒙班</text><text>启蒙阶段</text></view><view class="metrics"><view><text>班级容量</text><text>12人</text><text>满额16人</text></view><view><text>当前人数</text><text>12人</text><text>剩余4人</text></view><view><text>教练</text><text>李教练</text><text>5年教龄</text></view><view><text>课时</text><text>48课时</text><text>每课时60分钟</text></view></view></view><view class="fee"><text>¥2680</text><text>课程费用</text></view></view><view class="details"><view><image src="{{icons.calendar}}"/><text>上课时间</text><text>每周二、周四　17:00 - 18:00</text></view><view><image src="{{icons.location}}"/><text>上课地点</text><text>浦东校区 - 1号篮球馆</text></view><view><image src="{{icons.user}}"/><text>适合年龄</text><text>7-8岁</text></view><view><image src="{{icons.check}}"/><text>时间冲突检查</text><view><text>无冲突</text><text>已通过学员现有课程时间冲突检查</text></view></view></view></view>
<view class="section-title"><view class="mini">铃</view><text>通知设置</text></view><view class="notify"><view><image src="{{icons.user}}"/><view><text>通知教练</text><text>分班成功后，系统将自动通知教练</text></view><switch checked="{{notifyCoach}}" color="#ff7100" bindchange="toggleCoach"/></view><view><image src="{{icons.user}}"/><view><text>通知家长</text><text>分班成功后，系统将发送短信/微信通知家长</text></view><switch checked="{{notifyParent}}" color="#ff7100" bindchange="toggleParent"/></view></view>
<button class="primary" bindtap="confirm">确认分班并通知</button><button class="secondary" bindtap="reselect">↻　重新选择</button><view class="safe"></view></view></scroll-view></view>
